135
00:21:35,840 --> 00:21:36,840
Jawabannya cukup,

136
00:21:36,930 --> 00:21:39,220
Pertunjukan Ramleela ini,
selama sembilan hari,

137
00:21:39,300 --> 00:21:43,300
